The paper discusses the application of formal methods to security, which is a primary concern in the field of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the development of formal methods, which falls under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of formal methods in software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL), as well as the potential for artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to aid in the application of formal methods to security.
